{"tid":1081054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周末風力增強巨型KAWS公仔頂唔順！ 大會宣佈明日提早結束香港站","createTime":"2019-03-28T04:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T05:52:56.000Z","uid":3090,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ce474c3873f5cf6e958e0dabde9b4f15d461e772","tid":1081054,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T04:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3faxd40.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3faxd40.png&h=88882d52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXwgFK1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXwgFK1.png&h=a3f358f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZMjFnYn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZMjFnYn.png&h=0f987ab7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pDyCqbJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpDyCqbJ.png&h=9a72a994&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國藝術家KAWS的標誌性icon COMPANION，《KAWS:HOLIDAY》第3站香港站於上周五起於中西區海濱長廊（中環段）對開海面展示，原定於周日（3月31日）結束，但由於天文台預料未來周末將天氣不穩，為免影響巨型公仔的狀態和顧及海事工作人員安全，大會決定於明日（星期五）完成香港站的旅程提前「游走」。<br />\n<br />\n身長37米、全程保持躺臥姿態的COMPANION有着一雙「X X」的眼睛，是藝術家KAWS的標誌性設計，原於上周五（22日）展出至3月31日。不過主辦單位AllRightsReserved表示，由於香港天文台預測KAWS公仔預可承受4級風力，但天文台預期周六及日風力4至5級，而且更有雷雨。風力會對公仔造成很大拉扯，雨水也會令公仔造成壓力。為了避免COMPANION情況變差，步黃鴨當年後塵因漏氣而維修，同時也會增加海上工作的工作人員的風險，故宣佈3月29日提早結束香港站。"},{"pid":"d156ef5355601f800efe511c9b6996ad6282636d","tid":1081054,"uid":209301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T04:53:45.000Z","msg":"早走早著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6787dcdf49513bda6d4f4d3284b919caefa46ad2","tid":1081054,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T04:55:37.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7415f5172935ae61f4a8e44849941bcc576c38","tid":1081054,"uid":2772,"like":9,"dislike":2,"scor